I"Z<p>Overlay is a temporary layer covers on the content that shouldn’t be focused on.</p>

<h2 id="usage">Usage</h2>

<p>Use overlay when you have an important part of UI that needs users’ attention without getting distracted by the rest of the content. A pop-up window and an onboarding tour are the typical examples of using overlay.</p>

